00:57.858 --> 00:58.991
Mike:
Ah, homicide.

00:58.993 --> 01:00.659
What morning's complete

01:00.661 --> 01:03.762
Without a 100-yard hike
through garbage to a dead body?

01:03.764 --> 01:04.830
You picked up.

01:04.832 --> 01:06.432
When i pick up,

01:06.434 --> 01:09.902
The crime scene is a fountain
or a museum, someplace nice.

01:09.904 --> 01:12.404
You pick up,
it's a crack den or a tunnel.

01:12.406 --> 01:14.873
What?
I got bad crime-scene karma?

01:14.875 --> 01:16.608
[ chuckles ]
i'm just saying.

01:16.610 --> 01:19.178
No purse, no i.D.

01:19.180 --> 01:22.581
Someone liked
to take pictures, though.

01:22.583 --> 01:24.516
What do you think?
She a pro?

01:26.353 --> 01:28.987
Well, it wouldn't be the first
